column18: How did the quality damage affect your experience?
column19: Is our guideline clear? Please tell us anything you got confused with.

column18: Freeze greatly hurts my experience while blurring does as well but to a lesser extent.
The freezing makes me distracted and want to stop watching video cause it's irritating.
I had to wait until the video start, so it was little annoying
column19: Yes, but the score standard was kind of hard to understand, like I was not sure what do you expect for the score 1 and 5.

column18: It mildly affected my experience, especially in the videos where there is lots of movement.
column19: I thought there would be only one video without buffering but I felt that there were multiple.

column18: It was not a big issue from my experience.
